 Nigerian Stock Exchange  The total volume of trades advanced by 72.8 per cent to 356.431 million units, valued at N5.763 billion, and exchanged in 5,040 deals.     
 
Transactions in the shares of Guaranty Trust Bank topped the activity chart with 46.158 million shares valued at N1.426 billion. FBN Holdings (FBNH) followed with 35.342 million shares worth N256.889 million, while Dangote Sugar Refinery traded 26.82 million shares valued at N510.527 million.
 
